  "ui": {
    "fixedSections": [
      {
        "title": "一、实验目的",
        "segments": [
          "1. 掌握用三线摆和扭摆测量转动惯量的原理和方法。2. 掌握扭摆法测量材料切变模量的原理，了解测量材料切变模量的基本方法。3. 掌握基本长度测量和时间测量仪器的正确使用方法。实验仪器三线摆，扭摆，螺旋测微计。"
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "二、实验原理",
        "segments": [
          "1.三线摆：如图一，上、下圆盘均处于水平，悬挂在横梁上。横梁由立柱和底座支承着，三根对称分布的等长悬线将两个圆盘相连。上圆盘可以固定不动。拧动旋钮就可以使得下圆盘绕中心轴OO’作扭摆运动。当下圆盘的摆角很小且忽略空气阻力和悬线扭力影响时，可推出下圆盘绕中心轴OO’的转动惯量为：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_001.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "98.69908209396px",
            "height": "36.6266124958055px"
          },
          "其中，m₀是下圆盘质量，g取",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_002.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "64.7712726241613px",
            "height": "18.891621182047px"
          },
          "，r为上圆盘半径，R为下圆盘半径，H为平衡时上下圆盘的垂直距离，T₀为下圆盘摆动周期。",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_003.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "121.831679459732px",
            "height": "220.145218264262px"
          },
          "将质量为m的待测刚体放在下圆盘上，并使它的质心位于中心轴OO’上，测出此时的摆动周期T和上下圆盘之间的垂直距离H₁，则待测刚体和下圆盘对于中心轴OO’的总转动惯量J₁为：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_004.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "136.867867747484px",
            "height": "47.4218245998324px"
          },
          "且待测刚体对于中心轴OO’的转动惯量",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_005.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "70.9399652550338px",
            "height": "20.4337943397652px"
          },
          "。2.扭摆：实验中使用的扭摆结构如右图（图2），根据刚体转动定理有：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_006.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "67.8556189395975px",
            "height": "23.9036839446309px"
          },
          "其中，M是悬线因扭转产生的弹性恢复力矩，J₀为刚体对于悬线轴的转动惯量，",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_007.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "15.8072748666108px",
            "height": "14.6506449983222px"
          },
          "为角加速度。弹性恢复力矩M与转角",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_008.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "12.337385261745px",
            "height": "15.8072748666108px"
          },
          "的关系为：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_009.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "53.2382018131272px",
            "height": "13.489409243191px"
          },
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_010.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "104.482231435403px",
            "height": "161.542638270974px"
          },
          "其中，K为扭转模量，它与悬线长度L，悬线直径d及悬线材料的切变模量G有如下关系：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_011.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "74.02431157047px",
            "height": "39.7109588112417px"
          },
          "扭摆运动的微分方程为：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_012.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "74.02431157047px",
            "height": "40.0965021006713px"
          },
          "可见，圆盘作简谐运动，其周期为：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_013.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "81.3496340696311px",
            "height": "45.8796514421142px"
          },
          "本实验中K未知，所以用一个对质心轴转动惯量为J₁的附加物体加到盘上，并使其质心位于扭摆悬线上，组成复合体。此复合体对于悬线轴的转动惯量为",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_014.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "47.8073678892619px",
            "height": "18.891621182047px"
          },
          "，复合体的摆动周期T为：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_015.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "105.253318014262px",
            "height": "45.8796514421142px"
          },
          "因此得到：",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_016.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "99.0846253833896px",
            "height": "43.5663917055371px"
          },
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_017.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "97.5424522256714px",
            "height": "44.7230215738256px"
          },
          "测出T₀和T后就可以计算盘的转动惯量J₀和悬线的切变模量G。"
        ]
      }
    ],
